"<h1>頁面源代碼</h1>\n\n<div class=\"page-source\">\n\t[[iftags +組件]]<br />\n[[&gt;]]<br />\n[[module Rate]]<br />\n[[/&gt;]]<br />\n<br />\n[[module CSS]]<br />\n/* ---- PRESENTATION ---- */<br />\n&nbsp;.unmargined &gt; div:first-of-type{ display: none; }<br />\n&nbsp;.templateInfo{ margin: 0 0 1em; padding: 0 1em; border: 1px solid hsl(0, 0%, 87%); }<br />\n&nbsp;.templateInfo hr{ margin: 1em 0; }<br />\n&nbsp;h1, h3{ text-align: center; }<br />\n<br />\n/* ---- CODE BY WOEDENAZ ---- */<br />\n&nbsp;.help{<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;display: flex;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;align-content: stretch;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;padding-top: 1em;<br />\n}<br />\n&nbsp;.help blockquote{<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;margin: 0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;font-size: 85%;<br />\n}<br />\n&nbsp;.help blockquote &gt; p{<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;display: flex;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;flex-wrap: wrap;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;align-items: center;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;align-content: center;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;min-height: 2rem;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;margin: 0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;margin-right: 0;<br />\n}<br />\n&nbsp;.help blockquote &gt; p *{<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;height: 100%;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;margin: 0 .1rem;<br />\n}<br />\n&nbsp;.help blockquote:nth-of-type(1){<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;margin-right: 0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;padding: 0;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;background: transparent;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;border: unset;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;box-shadow: unset;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;text-align: right;<br />\n}<br />\n&nbsp;.help blockquote:nth-of-type(1) &gt; p{<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;justify-content: flex-end;<br />\n}<br />\n&nbsp;.help blockquote:nth-of-type(2){<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;width: 60%;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;margin-left: 1em;<br />\n}<br />\n[[/module]]<br />\n<br />\n[[note]]<br />\n**原作者：**<br />\n[[*user Lt Flops]]<br />\n----<br />\n**基於以下這位的成果而成的：**<br />\n[[*user Woedenaz]] ([[[*https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/anomaly-classification-system-guide|Source]]])<br />\n----<br />\n**如何使用：**<br />\nhttp://scp-zh-tr.wikidot.com/component:flops-header#toc2<br />\n[[/note]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;templateInfo&quot;]]<br />\n+ 範例<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[include <a href=\"http://scp-zh-tr.wikidot.com/component:flops-header-source\">:scp-zh-tr:component:flops-header-source</a><br />\n|item=0001<br />\n|containment=neutralized<br />\n|level=1<br />\n|security=unrestricted<br />\n|disruption=dark<br />\n|disruption-bg-color=hsl(197, 100%, 27%)<br />\n]]<br />\n<br />\n[[include <a href=\"http://scp-zh-tr.wikidot.com/component:flops-header-source\">:scp-zh-tr:component:flops-header-source</a><br />\n|item=0002<br />\n|containment=safe<br />\n|level=2<br />\n|security=restricted<br />\n|disruption=vlam<br />\n|disruption-bg-color=hsl(160, 100%, 27%)<br />\n]]<br />\n<br />\n[[include <a href=\"http://scp-zh-tr.wikidot.com/component:flops-header-source\">:scp-zh-tr:component:flops-header-source</a><br />\n|item=0003<br />\n|containment=euclid<br />\n|level=3<br />\n|security=confidential<br />\n|disruption=keneq<br />\n|disruption-bg-color=hsl(50, 100%, 37%)<br />\n]]<br />\n<br />\n[[include <a href=\"http://scp-zh-tr.wikidot.com/component:flops-header-source\">:scp-zh-tr:component:flops-header-source</a><br />\n|item=0004<br />\n|containment=keter<br />\n|level=4<br />\n|security=secret<br />\n|disruption=ekhi<br />\n|disruption-bg-color=hsl(26, 100%, 37%)<br />\n]]<br />\n<br />\n[[include <a href=\"http://scp-zh-tr.wikidot.com/component:flops-header-source\">:scp-zh-tr:component:flops-header-source</a><br />\n|item=0005<br />\n|containment=[*https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/esoteric-classes-complete-list apollyon]<br />\n|level=5<br />\n|security=top-secret<br />\n|disruption=amida<br />\n|disruption-bg-color=hsla(345, 100%, 27%)<br />\n]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;templateInfo&quot;]]<br />\n+ 這是啥？<br />\n----<br />\n一個基於SCP格式的簡單標頭樣式，有著以安保機密權限等級調整和簡單明瞭的瓦解等級條<br />\n<br />\n**[[[*http://scp-zh-tr.wikidot.com/anomaly-classification-system-guide#secondary-class|看這個頁面以獲得更多資訊]]]**<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;templateInfo&quot;]]<br />\n+ 如何使用<br />\n----<br />\n+++ 第一步，把這段貼到你的頁面上！<br />\n----<br />\n[[div class=&quot;code&quot;]]<br />\n@@[[include :scp-zh-tr:component:flops-header@@<br />\n@@|item=@@<br />\n@@|containment=@@<br />\n@@|level=@@<br />\n@@|security=@@<br />\n@@|disruption=@@<br />\n@@|disruption-bg-color=@@<br />\n@@]]@@<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n----<br />\n+++ 第二步，讀這個簡短的說明<br />\n----<br />\n[[div_ class=&quot;help&quot;]]<br />\n&gt; Include語法區塊的起點 ▷<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; 項目編號 ▷<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; 項目/收容 等級 ▷ **(會以英文大寫顯示)**<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; 機密等級 – 等級數字(1-6) ▷<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; 機密等級 – 安全類別名稱 ▷ **(會以英文大寫顯示)**<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; 瓦解等級名稱 ▷ **(會以英文大寫顯示)**<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; 指定資訊條的顏色 ▷ **(16進位, RGB, &amp; HSL 色碼都能用)**<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; Include語法區塊的終點 ▷<br />\n&gt; <br />\n<br />\n&gt; [[include :scp-zh-tr:component:flops-header<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; |item={{0001–9999}}<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; |containment={{safe}}/{{euclid}}/{{keter}}/{{thaumiel}}/{{other}}<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; |level={{1–6}}<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; |security={{unrestricted}}/{{restricted}}/{{confidential}}/{{secret}}/{{top-secret}}/{{other}}<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; |disruption={{dark}}/{{vlam}}/{{keneq}}/{{ekhi}}/{{amida}}/{{other}}<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; |disruption-bg-color={{#00638a}}/{{#008a5c}}/{{#bd9d00}}/{{#bd5200}}/{{#8a0022}}/{{your choice}}<br />\n&gt; <br />\n&gt; ]]<br />\n&gt; <br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n----<br />\n+++ 第三步，在每個=後面填入資訊<br />\n----<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[div class=&quot;templateInfo&quot;]]<br />\n+ 結果<br />\n[[/div]]<br />\n<br />\n[[include <a href=\"http://scp-zh-tr.wikidot.com/component:flops-header-source\">:scp-zh-tr:component:flops-header-source</a><br />\n|item=0000<br />\n|containment=thaumiel<br />\n|level=6<br />\n|security=the council<br />\n|disruption=undetermined<br />\n|disruption-bg-color=hsl(240, 15%, 37%)<br />\n]]<br />\n<br />\n@@ @@<br />\n----<br />\n+++ &gt; [[[https://scp-zh-tr.wikidot.com/component:flops-header-source|點我看原始碼！]]] &lt;<br />\n----<br />\n@@ @@<br />\n[[/iftags]]<br />\n<br />\n[[iftags -組件]]<br />\n[[include <a href=\"http://scp-zh-tr.wikidot.com/component:flops-header-source\">:scp-zh-tr:component:flops-header-source</a><br />\n|item={$item}<br />\n|containment={$containment}<br />\n|level={$level}<br />\n|security={$security}<br />\n|disruption={$disruption}<br />\n|disruption-bg-color={$disruption-bg-color}<br />\n]]<br />\n[[/iftags]]\n</div>\n"